steps.title: I logged in as a "CTDrug1" user with access to "Bazooka" project
I click on "Explore Menu" link on new Home Page

I navigate to "Competitive Landscape Viewer" page
I click on tab "Indication" in 'CI Landscape' page
I input a Query "Abdominal pain" into the "Indication" Look up text box in 'CI Landscape'
I select term "Abdominal pain" from 'Select from those listed below' box on pop-up 'look up' on 'Landscape' page
I click on button 'Prediction' on page 'Results' navigating from CLV
I verify a new pop-up 'Success Predictor' is opened
